'''Blossom Chukwujekwu''' yin aihundatọ [[Naijilia]] tọn, he basi dohia aihun etọn titan. To owhe 2015 ẹ mon àjò he yọn hugan yi to [[Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards]].

==Bẹjeji gbẹzan etọn tọn po wepiplọn po==
E ji chukwudi Echezoma Chukwujekwu to Abọ̀húsun azan ẹnẹtọ owhe 1983 to [[Benin City]], [[Edo]] to [[Nigeria|Naijilia]] to Dr. I. E po Evangelist J. C. Chukwujekwu, 
Blossom Chukwujekwu wẹ yin visunnu tintan to visunnu awe he mẹjitọ etọn ji lẹ me. Ogbe [[Otolo]] to Anambra Huwaji-agewaji [[Nigeria|Naijilia]] tọn. E yi Greater Tomorrow Primary School po Greater Tomorrow Comprehensive College to Benin City, [[Edo]]. Na nuhe du Wehọmẹ daho etọn e de nado yí plọn Mass Communication to Anambra to [[University of Science and Technology]] fie e zan owhe dopo te. E fo Wepiplọn etọn to [[Benson Idahosa University]] to Benin City, Edo whenue e ko zan whenu pẹde to University to Enugu.
Bọ to BIU, e yin ogàn na plipli ogbe Mass Communication ton (AMSCOS) to owhe 2007 jẹ 2008. E yin dopo to hagbe gbesọnọ to Popular House of Theartre (H. O. T) fie e yin nukọntọ to aihun lọ, Godless: The path to dawn. Blossom hen otẹn etọn Ukemu to aihun lọ Godless nado no viavi. 
To liyasun owhe 2008, e yi gbedewema pò Bachelor of Science degree to Mass Communications sọn Benson Idahosa University, Benin City, Edo State. 
E be jẹ Awọnlin to Naijilia, to osun pede gbedewema etọn yíyí godo nado basi National Youth Service Corps Obligation. 
Blossom nọ Awọnlin nado doafọna aihundida zọ́n etọn. 


